snippet.title: "They Forced Me" Ellen SPEAKS On Being Forced To CANCEL Her Show
snippet.description:
"They Forced Me" Ellen SPEAKS On Being Forced To CANCEL Her Show

It’s been a while since Ellen DeGeneres got exposed for being “the meanest person alive” and running a toxic workplace where employees were allegedly regularly mistreated.
After months of trying to deflect, deny, and shift blame onto others, Ellen was finally forced to cancel her show.
The fans are now saying the show's end was inevitable and a long time coming, but how did the former “Queen of Nice” react to getting canceled?
